results.name: Regular tetrangle where T(n,k,i) is the number of nonnegative integer matrices up to row and column permutations with no zero rows or columns and k nonzero entries summing to n, with i columns.
xref: Triangle sums are A007716. Triangle of row sums is A320801. Triangle of column sums is A317533. Triangle of last columns (without its leading column 1,0,0,0,...) is A055884.
